data.description: 3bd/2ba home with two car carport, providing country living at its best. As you step inside, you will notice this spacious and well-maintained home. Spacious yard totaling 1.7 acres in all, making it great for animals and children. This piece of paradise is located in a rural setting in the small town of St. Stephen. This is the perfect time to take advantage of a residence in a growing community in Berkeley County. Property is conveniently located close to Hwy 52. Included in this listing are 0470002089. Property is located in the perfect spot. This home has a 12x12 screened-in porch for those breezy afternoons.
